title: 2D Impossible Run
description:
Impossible Run is hard Arcade game for Android users. With just one control, tapping the screen to jump, guide your green square over spikes and jump onto blocks to get to the best score.
*Completely free
*No additional fees
*Auto generate level
*Unlimited level

Google Play link: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.bulstudios.impossiblerun
